document_data.Notable Players:
* [[Gwayne|Gwayne the Gamester]], a swindler in Ravens Bluff, performed the shell game and kept its components on standby in his thief's kit.<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/105/The Living City: Misti's Moonlight Pawnshop|18}}
* [[Raul|Raul the Shellman]], a [[human]] thief who offered the shell game to passersby in the Ravens Bluff market.
* The [[Sanctuary of Mask]], one of the guildhouses of the [[Night Masks]] in [[Westgate]],<ref>{{Cite dungeon/19/House of Cards|44}} had an entire room dedicated to teaching its members various types of con games, such as the shell game.<ref>{{Cite dungeon/19/House of Cards|49}}
